# Session state — local, per-machine, regenerated on each session-start.
# Ignore everything inside .harness-state/ EXCEPT triage-log.md (audit trail
# for /triage-parking, meant to persist across machines per the skill's
# always-log invariant). File-level patterns are required because gitignore
# cannot re-include a file whose parent directory is excluded.
.harness-state/*
!.harness-state/triage-log.md

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Editor
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
